snippet: A military plane crashed in Liberia on Monday, killing 11 people, including Guinea’s military chief and top officers, officials said.
abstract: Military plane crashes in Liberia, killing 11 people, including Guinea's military chief Gen Souleymane Kelefa Diallo.
lead_paragraph: A military plane crashed in Liberia on Monday, killing 11 people, including Guinea’s military chief and top officers, officials said.
